modDescription:
Don’t like noisy, wobbly [auger](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-tools/)? Here’s your solution, the noise is gone and the wobble is barely noticeable. The other tweaks are a higher capacity fuel tank and durability.

**[Download](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1r7Zb14znYX0bbbZeUVc1oIM3jbFqIVEq/view?usp=sharing)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/21494-alucards-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Noisy Pants](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/noisy-pants/)
